snippet.title: 『XALADIA: Rise of the Space Pirates X2』First Look Trailer
snippet.description:
Upgrade your weapons, take control of your arms, and annihilate alien enemies with style in XALADIA - the newest twin-stick shooter game!

『XALADIA: Rise of the Space Pirates X2』arrives on 2023 on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5, and PC. 

Steam  ：https://store.steampowered.com/app/2218190/XALADIA_Rise_of_the_Space_Pirates_X2/
Discord：https://discord.gg/ajawXaQqnK
Twitter ：https://twitter.com/astargames_en
